race.description: Tabtouch Try Bet Loop Today (Bm58+) Handicap
race.comment: SKYTALKER (3) is knocking on the door of another win, finishing 2.5L off the winner last start at Albany. The slight rise in trip should suit and the visors go on for the first time. There's plenty to like about him and he looks ready to return to winning ways. MA MA BELLE (6) made it back-to-back wins last start at Pinjarra when holding on to score in a photo finish. Nottle remains in the saddle and she has the speed to work across from out wide. In form now and can extend her winning streak. MAGIC MIKEY (7) comes here on the fresh side after a slightly disappointing run 64 days ago. Faithfull rides now who has had success when partnering in the past. Needs some luck from out wide but has the figures to feature if the breaks come. CHIMINY BLUE (9) was too good at Albany last start and can go on with the job. BEST OF THE GODS (4) can feature first-up.
